een to this zone for a *very* long time. leveled all my characters on another server there. i dont have a problem with sharing this camp (although you really cant share orcs effectively). <br>but you DONT show up and start hitting on those orcs if there is a FULL group around. no matter if you are level 20+. ask for getting on the waiting list or get the hell outta there. go into the castle. go solo gnolls. go to another zone. plus, you dont bitch at the people there. and stop whining if your ass is getting beaten from your suckhead-pulls. <br><br>the point is:<br><br>Full Group &gt; You<br><br>if you are capable of soloing the whole orc camp, then you are already too high.<br><br>i dont petition there. did this before. GM will tell you to share the camp. this is not the problem. the behaviour is! <br>so last night another 2 fine players have made it on my personal shit list. grats!<br><br>i dont think this will ever change but i needed to get it out of my system... <br><br><br><br> <p><HTML><BODY><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/04/01/flamingtext_com_1017689407_15956.gif" </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukloeviseq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KloevisEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/12/02 11:31:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=531.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.cci.clarku.edu/ebarry/pix1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Idiots in Highpass /sigh</span><hr size=1> same problem a few nights ago.<br>people think that just because they make the annoying trip to the HH area, they aren't gonna leave until they group.<br><br>if you're gonna trave